- next needs: intake to produce `brief.json` capturing BROCCOLI first-word rule, the 3 application questions, ethics/rate-limit constraints, required per-lot fields, Americas/budget/video, and Michael's U.S. Bank + Python/Puppeteer/Playwright angle as explicit graded items.
- risks: live scraping flakiness/legality → restrict to scrape-friendly public sources + cached fallback; missing public GitHub scraper to link → may need to publish demo scraper source; full-stack misframing → keep specialist positioning.
